ActMarine Liability Act
PrecisAppointment of CAROLINE HEALEY of Montréal, Quebec, to be the Administrator of the Ship-source Oil Pollution Fund and the Fund for Railway Accidents Involving Designated Goods, to hold office during good behaviour on a full-time basis for a term of five years, in the place of Mark A.
